&lt;p class=&quot;p8i6j01 paragraph&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Vonage Communications APIs&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p8i6j01 paragraph&quot;&gt;As an emerging leader in the $10B+ communications API market, we empower global brands to connect better with their customers, employees, and partners through transformative communications experiences. For example, Vonage API solutions empower organizations to build their custom omnichannel communications structure. This allows them to reach and engage customers on their preferred schedule and channel, including voice, video, and messaging. Think of a rideshare service instantly connecting with customers, hospital staff conducting remote monitoring, customers verifying their identity before completing a purchase, AI virtual agents servicing customers around the clock, and much more.&lt;/p&gt;
