&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Join Vonage and help us innovate cloud communications for businesses worldwide!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Vonage is currently looking for a Deal Desk Analyst, based in Mexico who will provide direct support &amp;amp; guidance to the Sales Teams in all commercial aspects of deals with existing and prospective customers, including pricing quotations. The candidate will lead the commercial execution of complex, high-value deals and act as a strategic advisor responsible for bringing together Sales, Marketing, Operations, Product, Finance, and Legal team members to develop and execute Vonage’s pricing strategy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your contribution will be essential to win deals, increase Vonage market share and grow the revenue stream.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with the Sales Teams in building price quotes for customers, including our largest and most strategic accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze deal margins and competitive positioning to ensure we are winning deals and market share without sacrificing long-term financial health.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Actively collaborate with Operations, Finance, Legal, Product and Pricing teams to optimize the on-boarding experience of customers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help drive the adoption of CPQ, the Sales self-service quoting tool in SFDC.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Transform raw deal data into actionable insights, identifying pricing trends and competitive shifts to influence Vonage’s global pricing strategy.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Streamline and improve business practices, including tools, templates and processes, to increase the efficiency of the Deal Desk team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Train and advise Sales and any other stakeholders on pricing, quoting, on-boarding process and commercial best practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and manage projects to deliver further operational efficiencies and deal velocity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Desired Skills and Experience&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree required; Business, Economics, Finance or Accounting undergrad majors preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years in a Strategic Deal Desk, Sales Operations, or Commercial Finance role within a fast-paced SaaS or Telecom environment.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Salesforce (SFDC) and CPQ environments.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Problem solving&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent Excel skills and data manipulation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluent in English&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Personal Characteristics&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are a self-starter, an initiator&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Customer-focused - Always thinks first about the needs of their internal customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are delivery-focused&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are curious and informed - Stays on top of the latest in product, pricing, and industry news&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are structured in your approach&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have an innovative mindset and consistently challenge existing norms to drive improvement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have a team first mentality and put the company objectives ahead of your own&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable in a fast pace, global &amp;amp; multicultural environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;There’s no perfect candidate.&lt;/strong&gt; You don&#39;t need all the preferred qualifications to make a valuable impact on our team. Our employees and customers come from diverse backgrounds, so if you&#39;re passionate about what you could achieve at Vonage, we&#39;d love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
