&lt;p&gt;As the Director of Product for BSS &amp;amp; Platform Services, you will be accountable for driving Vonage’s product strategy for the shared platform capabilities that span across Lead-to-cash (BSS), Data Analytics, Identity Management, Accounts &amp;amp; Users and API Gateway. You will lead and guide a team of product managers focused on evolving and transforming our critical shared and platform services for both internal and external users, from sales, commercial and revenue operations to developers and customers.&lt;/p&gt;
