&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your key responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take comprehensive ownership of the Lead-to-Cash (BSS), Data analytics, Identity, Accounts &amp;amp; users and API gateway product offering in terms of product strategy, product capabilities, competitiveness and differentiation, profitability, compliance, certifications, security and architectural evolution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and execute product strategy, including the evolution of AI integrations and capabilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operationally manage the team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with other Portfolio Leaders, Product Managers, Sales &amp;amp; Marketing leaders, Carrier Team &amp;amp;&amp;nbsp; Engineering Leadership.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;As Product Director of a large shared service Product line, you will be responsible for constant prioritization and trade offs across all product lines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive development speed and efficiency in collaboration with Engineering and Operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide strong stewardship of the digital transformation of our business support systems and new back-office services integration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
